1
00:00:51,583 --> 00:00:52,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孙悟空你这个畜牲</font></font></font>

2
00:00:52,833 --> 00:00:54,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你本来答应如来佛祖</font></font></font>

3
00:00:54,500 --> 00:00:57,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">护送你师父唐三藏去取西经</font></font></font>

4
00:00:57,625 --> 00:01:01,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你竟然跟牛魔王串通要吃你师父</font></font></font>

5
00:01:01,792 --> 00:01:02,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">少啰嗦</font></font></font>

6
00:01:04,458 --> 00:01:05,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你追了我三日三夜</font></font></font>

7
00:01:06,375 --> 00:01:07,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因为你是女人，我才不杀你</font></font></font>

8
00:01:08,583 --> 00:01:09,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要以为我怕你啊</font></font></font>

9
00:01:10,792 --> 00:01:11,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空</font></font></font>

10
00:01:12,167 --> 00:01:14,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你怎么可以这样跟观音姐姐讲话呢？</font></font></font>

11
00:01:16,542 --> 00:01:17,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要吵</font></font></font>

12
00:01:18,542 --> 00:01:19,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你又在吓我</font></font></font>

13
00:01:20,875 --> 00:01:23,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不是怕我</font></font></font>

14
00:01:23,833 --> 00:01:25,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">又为什么要打伤紫霞仙子？</font></font></font>

15
00:01:25,458 --> 00:01:26,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">抢了她的月光宝盒呢？</font></font></font>

16
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:28,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不就是想躲开我嘛</font></font></font>

17
00:01:29,875 --> 00:01:30,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">唉！既然躲不了</font></font></font>

18
00:01:31,042 --> 00:01:33,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">老孙只有跟你决一死战</font></font></font>

19
00:01:34,208 --> 00:01:35,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要干什么？</font></font></font>

20
00:01:37,250 --> 00:01:38,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大家不要生气</font></font></font>

21
00:01:38,750 --> 00:01:40,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">生气会犯了嗔戒的</font></font></font>

22
00:01:40,417 --> 00:01:42,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空，你也太调皮了</font></font></font>

23
00:01:42,667 --> 00:01:43,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我跟你说过</font></font></font>

24
00:01:43,792 --> 00:01:45,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">叫你不要乱扔东西这么脏</font></font></font>

25
00:01:45,333 --> 00:01:47,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你看！</font></font></font>

26
00:01:47,667 --> 00:01:49,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我还未说完，你把棍子又给扔掉了</font></font></font>

27
00:01:49,500 --> 00:01:51,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">月光宝盒是宝物</font></font></font>

28
00:01:51,125 --> 00:01:53,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你把它扔掉会染污环境</font></font></font>

29
00:01:54,792 --> 00:01:56,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要是砸着小朋友那怎么办？</font></font></font>

30
00:01:56,292 --> 00:01:57,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就算没有砸着小朋友</font></font></font>

31
00:01:57,458 --> 00:02:00,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">砸着那些花花草草也是不对的</font></font></font>

32
00:02:02,458 --> 00:02:03,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">干什么？</font></font></font>

33
00:02:03,583 --> 00:02:04,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">放手？</font></font></font>

34
00:02:05,125 --> 00:02:06,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你想要？</font></font></font>

35
00:02:06,208 --> 00:02:09,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空，你想要就说话嘛！</font></font></font>

36
00:02:09,125 --> 00:02:12,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不说我怎么知道你想要呢？</font></font></font>

37
00:02:12,708 --> 00:02:14,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">虽然你很有诚意的看着我</font></font></font>

38
00:02:14,750 --> 00:02:16,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是你还是要跟我说你想要的</font></font></font>

39
00:02:16,750 --> 00:02:18,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那你拿去吧</font></font></font>

40
00:02:18,167 --> 00:02:19,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不是真的想要吧？</font></font></font>

41
00:02:19,792 --> 00:02:20,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">难道你真是想要吗？</font></font></font>

42
00:02:20,792 --> 00:02:21,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我拷！</font></font></font>

43
00:02:23,625 --> 00:02:24,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孙悟空…</font></font></font>

44
00:02:27,125 --> 00:02:27,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大家看到啦</font></font></font>

45
00:02:28,417 --> 00:02:29,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个家伙没事就长篇大论</font></font></font>

46
00:02:29,833 --> 00:02:31,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">婆婆妈妈，叽叽歪歪</font></font></font>

47
00:02:31,708 --> 00:02:33,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就好像整天有一只苍蝇</font></font></font>

48
00:02:36,125 --> 00:02:37,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对不起，不是一只</font></font></font>

49
00:02:37,958 --> 00:02:40,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是一堆苍蝇围着你</font></font></font>

50
00:02:44,625 --> 00:02:46,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还飞到你的耳朵里面</font></font></font>

51
00:02:48,167 --> 00:02:50,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">救命呀！</font></font></font>

52
00:02:54,583 --> 00:02:56,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">救命呀！</font></font></font>

53
00:02:59,250 --> 00:03:01,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">所以呢我抓住这只苍蝇挤破它肚皮</font></font></font>

54
00:03:01,333 --> 00:03:02,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把它的肠子扯出来</font></font></font>

55
00:03:02,417 --> 00:03:03,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">再用它的肠子勒着它的脖子</font></font></font>

56
00:03:04,042 --> 00:03:05,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">用力一拉</font></font></font>

57
00:03:07,125 --> 00:03:09,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">各位，整条舌头都伸出来了</font></font></font>

58
00:03:10,125 --> 00:03:10,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我再手起刀落</font></font></font>

59
00:03:10,917 --> 00:03:11,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哗！</font></font></font>

60
00:03:15,250 --> 00:03:18,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">整个世界清静了</font></font></font>

61
00:03:20,792 --> 00:03:27,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现在大家明白为什么我要杀它啦</font></font></font>

62
00:03:28,208 --> 00:03:30,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">悟空，你诸多借口</font></font></font>

63
00:03:30,708 --> 00:03:32,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你根本不想去取西经</font></font></font>

64
00:03:33,417 --> 00:03:35,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">说那么多干什么，打吧！</font></font></font>

65
00:03:51,250 --> 00:03:52,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我老孙有金刚不坏之身</font></font></font>

66
00:03:52,875 --> 00:03:54,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">十个观世音都不放在眼里</font></font></font>

67
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:09,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天我要替天行道</font></font></font>

68
00:04:10,167 --> 00:04:12,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">徒弟有错，做师父的也有责任</font></font></font>

69
00:04:12,708 --> 00:04:14,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">求姐姐放他一条生路吧！</font></font></font>

70
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:17,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不消灭他，我无法同玉皇大帝交代</font></font></font>

71
00:04:18,042 --> 00:04:19,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">求姐姐跟玉皇大帝说一声</font></font></font>

72
00:04:19,875 --> 00:04:22,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">贫僧愿意一命赔一命</font></font></font>

73
00:04:29,333 --> 00:04:30,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">唐三藏</font></font></font>

74
00:04:33,083 --> 00:04:37,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">喃呒阿弥陀佛…</font></font></font>

75
00:06:43,917 --> 00:06:45,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">到底他想说什么？</font></font></font>

76
00:06:51,083 --> 00:06:52,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">给他块肉</font></font></font>

77
00:06:53,792 --> 00:06:54,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大家小心点！</font></font></font>

78
00:06:54,917 --> 00:06:56,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">外面有个女人来</font></font></font>

79
00:06:56,167 --> 00:06:58,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">二当家，你猜会不会是官兵呢？</font></font></font>

80
00:06:58,708 --> 00:07:00,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怪不得人家叫你瞎子啦</font></font></font>

81
00:07:01,458 --> 00:07:03,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你没看到哑巴屁股扭来扭去的吗？</font></font></font>

82
00:07:04,375 --> 00:07:06,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">扭来扭去的说不定长生痔疮呀？</font></font></font>

83
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就算是有</font></font></font>

84
00:07:08,208 --> 00:07:10,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">也是个长痔疮的官兵</font></font></font>

85
00:07:10,625 --> 00:07:11,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怕什么？</font></font></font>

86
00:07:38,958 --> 00:07:39,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么人？</font></font></font>

87
00:07:40,458 --> 00:07:43,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">难道各位看不出我是个女人吗？</font></font></font>

88
00:07:46,333 --> 00:07:47,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你来这里干什么？</font></font></font>

89
00:07:50,000 --> 00:07:52,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">世途险恶，北风凛然</font></font></font>

90
00:07:52,375 --> 00:07:53,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一个弱小女子</font></font></font>

91
00:07:53,583 --> 00:07:55,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">想找一个栖身之所歇息一下</font></font></font>

92
00:07:55,333 --> 00:07:56,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">洗洗身上的风尘</font></font></font>

93
00:07:58,208 --> 00:08:00,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你知不知道这里是什么地方？</font></font></font>

94
00:08:01,542 --> 00:08:04,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">此处乌烟瘴气，各位又面目狰狞</font></font></font>

95
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:07,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">绝不像是一家客栈</font></font></font>

96
00:08:07,917 --> 00:08:10,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">莫非是一间黑店？</font></font></font>

97
00:08:11,333 --> 00:08:13,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">明知是黑店你还敢进来</font></font></font>

98
00:08:14,500 --> 00:08:16,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不怕送羊入虎口吗？</font></font></font>

99
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁是羊？谁是虎？</font></font></font>

100
00:08:21,042 --> 00:08:22,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现在还言之过早</font></font></font>

101
00:08:23,375 --> 00:08:25,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果各位大爷是强盗</font></font></font>

102
00:08:26,500 --> 00:08:28,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">难道就不怕我是强盗头吗？</font></font></font>

103
00:08:30,333 --> 00:08:32,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你到底是何方神圣？</font></font></font>

104
00:08:42,208 --> 00:08:43,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">桃花</font></font></font>

105
00:08:44,458 --> 00:08:47,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">桃花过处，寸草不生</font></font></font>

106
00:08:47,458 --> 00:08:49,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">金钱落地，人头不保</font></font></font>

107
00:08:58,250 --> 00:09:01,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">春三十娘到五岳山来干什么呢？</font></font></font>

108
00:09:02,542 --> 00:09:05,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个女魔头一向无宝不到</font></font></font>

109
00:09:06,542 --> 00:09:10,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">难道这里会有大买卖？</font></font></font>

110
00:09:14,750 --> 00:09:15,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们这些笨蛋</font></font></font>

111
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:16,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还把银子顶在头上干什么？</font></font></font>

112
00:09:17,167 --> 00:09:18,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">放下来！</font></font></font>

113
00:09:18,167 --> 00:09:20,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不行！金钱落地，人头不保啊，帮主</font></font></font>

114
00:09:20,667 --> 00:09:21,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说什么？</font></font></font>

115
00:09:22,583 --> 00:09:25,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">二当家</font></font></font>

116
00:09:26,083 --> 00:09:27,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你这么没种怎么当我二当家？</font></font></font>

117
00:09:27,542 --> 00:09:30,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主，我不是二当家，我系瞎子啊</font></font></font>

118
00:09:30,667 --> 00:09:31,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他才是二当家啊！</font></font></font>

119
00:09:31,708 --> 00:09:33,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对啊！我才是二当家呀</font></font></font>

120
00:09:33,208 --> 00:09:34,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我骂瞎子是要你惭愧</font></font></font>

121
00:09:35,667 --> 00:09:36,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你还不跑！</font></font></font>

122
00:09:37,542 --> 00:09:40,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看看你的德性，鬼鬼祟崇，丢人现眼</font></font></font>

123
00:09:40,333 --> 00:09:41,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">披头散发！人模狗样</font></font></font>

124
00:09:41,500 --> 00:09:43,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么跟我出来闯荡江湖啊呀？呀？</font></font></font>

125
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:45,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主，我在这里啊！</font></font></font>

126
00:09:46,417 --> 00:09:47,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还不现身？</font></font></font>

127
00:09:47,667 --> 00:09:49,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现身了，帮主</font></font></font>

128
00:09:49,667 --> 00:09:51,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你中了昆仑三圣的七伤拳</font></font></font>

129
00:09:51,333 --> 00:09:52,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">现在伤势开始发作</font></font></font>

130
00:09:52,792 --> 00:09:53,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你还敢说</font></font></font>

131
00:09:53,875 --> 00:09:55,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那天不是你把脖子缩了一下</font></font></font>

132
00:09:55,125 --> 00:09:56,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我会被人家打中鼻子吗？</font></font></font>

133
00:09:56,875 --> 00:09:57,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这边啊，帮主</font></font></font>

134
00:09:58,625 --> 00:10:00,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">七伤拳把帮主害得真惨</font></font></font>

135
00:10:01,292 --> 00:10:04,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主，我当时是吓得跪下来嘛</font></font></font>

136
00:10:04,167 --> 00:10:05,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我听说中了七伤拳</font></font></font>

137
00:10:05,583 --> 00:10:06,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">首先是变斗鸡眼</font></font></font>

138
00:10:06,958 --> 00:10:08,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">然后耳朵失聪，聪不到声音</font></font></font>

139
00:10:08,958 --> 00:10:11,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">之后声线失控，说话全部都走音</font></font></font>

140
00:10:11,500 --> 00:10:13,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">最后五脏六腑爆炸，然后就死定了！</font></font></font>

141
00:10:13,583 --> 00:10:14,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主，你斗鸡眼很严重啊！</font></font></font>

142
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁说我斗鸡眼啊？</font></font></font>

143
00:10:16,167 --> 00:10:17,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我只是把视力集中在一点</font></font></font>

144
00:10:17,417 --> 00:10:19,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">以改变我以往对事物的看法！干嘛？</font></font></font>

145
00:10:19,458 --> 00:10:21,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">造谣我不行了，想抢我的位子呀？</font></font></font>

146
00:10:21,542 --> 00:10:22,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不敢帮主，不敢呀</font></font></font>

147
00:10:23,042 --> 00:10:25,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我踩死你，不敢</font></font></font>

148
00:10:25,375 --> 00:10:26,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我踩！</font></font></font>

149
00:10:26,667 --> 00:10:28,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我踩那么久，就算不痛也呻吟两声嘛</font></font></font>

150
00:10:28,667 --> 00:10:30,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">收到…啊！…</font></font></font>

151
00:10:31,625 --> 00:10:34,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好！大家准备带着家伙去找…</font></font></font>

152
00:10:34,208 --> 00:10:35,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">春三十娘</font></font></font>

153
00:10:36,833 --> 00:10:38,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怕什么！万事有我！</font></font></font>

154
00:10:44,125 --> 00:10:45,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在下斧头帮帮主</font></font></font>

155
00:10:45,542 --> 00:10:47,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">外号玉面飞龙至尊宝</font></font></font>

156
00:10:48,708 --> 00:10:51,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">久闻春三十娘大名，如雷贯耳</font></font></font>

157
00:10:51,625 --> 00:10:53,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">请问春三十娘光临敝帮</font></font></font>

158
00:10:53,292 --> 00:10:54,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有何贵干呢？</font></font></font>

159
00:10:56,000 --> 00:10:57,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我要在这个地方逗留片刻</font></font></font>

160
00:10:58,625 --> 00:11:00,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不知片刻是多久？</font></font></font>

161
00:11:00,667 --> 00:11:02,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">三天两夜</font></font></font>

162
00:11:04,250 --> 00:11:06,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">也有可能是三、五、十年</font></font></font>

163
00:11:06,458 --> 00:11:08,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">总之等到我要等的人出现</font></font></font>

164
00:11:08,208 --> 00:11:09,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就会离开</font></font></font>

165
00:11:11,292 --> 00:11:13,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我怕你没那么长命</font></font></font>

166
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你干什么？</font></font></font>

167
00:11:18,292 --> 00:11:19,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">小完便穿裤子</font></font></font>

168
00:11:20,333 --> 00:11:21,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你在这里小便？</font></font></font>

169
00:11:21,500 --> 00:11:23,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不然你哪来这么大缸水洗澡啊？</font></font></font>

170
00:11:23,875 --> 00:11:24,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说什么？</font></font></font>

171
00:11:25,125 --> 00:11:27,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我话你没那么长命等到你要见的人</font></font></font>

172
00:11:34,625 --> 00:11:36,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主…</font></font></font>

173
00:12:05,583 --> 00:12:06,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">想杀我没那么容易</font></font></font>

174
00:12:07,042 --> 00:12:08,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">先问过我的兄弟们</font></font></font>

175
00:12:11,875 --> 00:12:13,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没义气啊！</font></font></font>

176
00:12:15,250 --> 00:12:17,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们这些吃里扒外的家伙</font></font></font>

177
00:12:18,042 --> 00:12:19,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">天呀！</font></font></font>

178
00:12:20,792 --> 00:12:21,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">饶命呀…</font></font></font>

179
00:12:21,875 --> 00:12:23,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你有本事就把我们全杀光！</font></font></font>

180
00:12:26,333 --> 00:12:27,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">饶命呀，女英雄</font></font></font>

181
00:12:28,000 --> 00:12:32,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">白痴！你以为她就会放过你吗？</font></font></font>

182
00:12:32,417 --> 00:12:34,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">无论说什么也要跟她拼了</font></font></font>

183
00:12:34,667 --> 00:12:37,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">男儿膝下有黄金！既然他们肯求我</font></font></font>

184
00:12:38,333 --> 00:12:39,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那么性命暂时寄存在我这里</font></font></font>

185
00:12:40,458 --> 00:12:42,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谢谢女英雄！</font></font></font>

186
00:12:42,875 --> 00:12:46,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">至于你嘛…你可真有骨气</font></font></font>

187
00:12:56,125 --> 00:12:57,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孺子可教</font></font></font>

188
00:12:59,792 --> 00:13:01,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">叫他们把脚底板洗干净在外面等我</font></font></font>

189
00:13:09,167 --> 00:13:10,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么会有块疤？</font></font></font>

190
00:13:10,208 --> 00:13:11,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这不是疤啊，这只是肮脏啊</font></font></font>

191
00:13:11,792 --> 00:13:12,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">马上去洗干净</font></font></font>

192
00:13:12,792 --> 00:13:13,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不然的话我把它砍下来</font></font></font>

193
00:13:14,042 --> 00:13:15,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主啊</font></font></font>

194
00:13:15,417 --> 00:13:16,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她为什么要看我们的脚底板呢？</font></font></font>

195
00:13:16,792 --> 00:13:19,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">幸亏只是看脚板，而不是看屁股呢</font></font></font>

196
00:13:19,708 --> 00:13:20,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你怕啊？</font></font></font>

197
00:13:20,625 --> 00:13:21,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是你怕啊，不是我怕！</font></font></font>

198
00:13:22,042 --> 00:13:23,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为什么？</font></font></font>

199
00:13:23,083 --> 00:13:24,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你屁股长了那么多痱子</font></font></font>

200
00:13:24,125 --> 00:13:24,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">说不定会说你不干净</font></font></font>

201
00:13:24,917 --> 00:13:25,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要把它切掉啊！</font></font></font>

202
00:13:25,958 --> 00:13:26,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你怎么知道我屁股…</font></font></font>

203
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">瞎子说偷看你洗澡看到的</font></font></font>

204
00:13:29,333 --> 00:13:30,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你干嘛偷看我洗澡啊？</font></font></font>

205
00:13:31,500 --> 00:13:32,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不止偷看你一个</font></font></font>

206
00:13:32,500 --> 00:13:33,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">所有人我都偷看过了</font></font></font>

207
00:13:37,917 --> 00:13:38,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么会这么多毛啊？</font></font></font>

208
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:39,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">正常啊！</font></font></font>

209
00:13:40,042 --> 00:13:41,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我身体上其它地方的毛更茂盛</font></font></font>

210
00:13:41,958 --> 00:13:42,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么样？</font></font></font>

211
00:13:42,792 --> 00:13:44,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是不是看得你心痒痒？</font></font></font>

212
00:13:46,083 --> 00:13:47,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说那里长得更茂盛啊？</font></font></font>

213
00:13:48,583 --> 00:13:49,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不是呀！</font></font></font>

214
00:13:49,625 --> 00:13:51,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">其实我只是头上跟脚底板有毛</font></font></font>

215
00:13:51,542 --> 00:13:52,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大概是长错地方了</font></font></font>

216
00:13:54,958 --> 00:13:56,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">从今天起，我要你不分昼夜</font></font></font>

217
00:13:56,917 --> 00:13:58,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">查看所有经过这里的人</font></font></font>

218
00:13:59,708 --> 00:14:00,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">查什么？</font></font></font>

219
00:14:01,167 --> 00:14:02,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">查他们脚底板</font></font></font>

220
00:14:02,208 --> 00:14:04,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果发现有三颗痣的，立即通知我</font></font></font>

221
00:14:11,500 --> 00:14:13,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主呀！我们不是抢劫</font></font></font>

222
00:14:13,792 --> 00:14:15,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">光看人家的脚底板</font></font></font>

223
00:14:15,458 --> 00:14:18,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要是被同行知道，会笑我们变态啊</font></font></font>

224
00:14:19,208 --> 00:14:21,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">明刀明枪斗不过她，暗箭她就难防</font></font></font>

225
00:14:21,417 --> 00:14:23,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今夜三更用五毒迷晕香让她尝尝</font></font></font>

226
00:14:23,125 --> 00:14:24,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">先奸后杀！</font></font></font>

227
00:14:24,167 --> 00:14:25,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好计谋！</font></font></font>

228
00:14:25,542 --> 00:14:26,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你也觉得好吧</font></font></font>

229
00:14:26,917 --> 00:14:28,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个任务就交给你去执行</font></font></font>

230
00:14:28,417 --> 00:14:30,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这么看得起我，算了吧！</font></font></font>

231
00:14:30,583 --> 00:14:33,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不用了，帮主，不用下跪了</font></font></font>

232
00:14:33,333 --> 00:14:35,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你以为我想跪啊！是我的腿不听使唤</font></font></font>

233
00:14:35,833 --> 00:14:38,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主，你七伤拳的伤势越来越严重了</font></font></font>

234
00:14:38,667 --> 00:14:40,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我还有双手</font></font></font>

235
00:14:41,000 --> 00:14:42,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不会屈服的</font></font></font>

236
00:14:47,625 --> 00:14:48,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主掉粪坑去了</font></font></font>

237
00:14:49,042 --> 00:14:50,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主呀！</font></font></font>

238
00:15:33,167 --> 00:15:35,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你找到三颗痣没有啊？</font></font></font>

239
00:15:35,958 --> 00:15:37,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为什么每个人都叫我找三颗痣？</font></font></font>

240
00:15:37,792 --> 00:15:39,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">找到你就可以救他了</font></font></font>

241
00:15:40,333 --> 00:15:41,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说什么？</font></font></font>

242
00:15:41,417 --> 00:15:42,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这里到底是什么地方？</font></font></font>

243
00:15:42,958 --> 00:15:44,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么人？</font></font></font>

244
00:15:47,000 --> 00:15:48,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">做梦</font></font></font>

245
00:15:50,750 --> 00:15:52,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把那贱人干掉了是吗？</font></font></font>

246
00:15:58,167 --> 00:16:01,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">蜘蛛！蜘蛛呀！…</font></font></font>

247
00:16:02,333 --> 00:16:03,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">蜘蛛用得着大惊小怪的？</font></font></font>

248
00:16:03,625 --> 00:16:04,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好大只呀！</font></font></font>

249
00:16:04,958 --> 00:16:06,000
