377
00:23:26,667 --> 00:23:28,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大不了重伤！要死那么容易吗？</font></font></font>

378
00:23:32,792 --> 00:23:33,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">混蛋！</font></font></font>

379
00:23:37,167 --> 00:23:39,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">起来！你少在我前装蒜</font></font></font>

380
00:23:39,208 --> 00:23:40,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我告诉你</font></font></font>

381
00:23:40,958 --> 00:23:42,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">少来这一套</font></font></font>

382
00:23:43,917 --> 00:23:44,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真的晕倒了？</font></font></font>

383
00:23:45,000 --> 00:23:46,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大牛、二虎</font></font></font>

384
00:23:47,667 --> 00:23:50,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">散得真快，我自己来</font></font></font>

385
00:24:01,458 --> 00:24:02,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么样？</font></font></font>

386
00:24:02,625 --> 00:24:03,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你刚才真的装昏？</font></font></font>

387
00:24:05,833 --> 00:24:07,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这一招叫做忍辱偷生</font></font></font>

388
00:24:07,583 --> 00:24:09,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大腿捱一刀算得了什么？</font></font></font>

389
00:24:14,333 --> 00:24:15,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那儿漏水？</font></font></font>

390
00:24:16,958 --> 00:24:19,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">二当家，不是漏水，是你流血啦</font></font></font>

391
00:24:19,917 --> 00:24:21,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要怕…</font></font></font>

392
00:24:22,167 --> 00:24:24,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我只要点我曲池，疾宫两个穴道</font></font></font>

393
00:24:24,125 --> 00:24:25,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">血马上就停止</font></font></font>

394
00:24:42,458 --> 00:24:43,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这里算不上山明水秀</font></font></font>

395
00:24:43,958 --> 00:24:45,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是也别有一番风味</font></font></font>

396
00:24:45,667 --> 00:24:47,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">两位住在这里一定会爱上它</font></font></font>

397
00:24:47,833 --> 00:24:48,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晚安！</font></font></font>

398
00:24:54,667 --> 00:24:56,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主，怎么样？…</font></font></font>

399
00:24:56,292 --> 00:24:57,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么样？是不是妖怪？</font></font></font>

400
00:24:57,417 --> 00:24:58,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是！</font></font></font>

401
00:24:58,542 --> 00:24:59,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">而且非常的妖！</font></font></font>

402
00:25:00,292 --> 00:25:03,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">弄得我心卜通卜通乱跳</font></font></font>

403
00:25:04,125 --> 00:25:05,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主请留步</font></font></font>

404
00:25:09,958 --> 00:25:13,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师姐说，帮主大仁大义，是侠中之侠</font></font></font>

405
00:25:13,917 --> 00:25:15,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">能交上帮主你这样的朋友</font></font></font>

406
00:25:15,375 --> 00:25:16,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真是三生有幸</font></font></font>

407
00:25:17,292 --> 00:25:19,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天搁在你兄弟们头上的钱</font></font></font>

408
00:25:19,458 --> 00:25:21,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就当请大家去买酒喝吧</font></font></font>

409
00:25:22,000 --> 00:25:23,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">多谢三十娘一番美意</font></font></font>

410
00:25:25,917 --> 00:25:27,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主，品味太差了吧？</font></font></font>

411
00:25:28,042 --> 00:25:29,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">各有所好嘛</font></font></font>

412
00:25:34,292 --> 00:25:37,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大腿扎一刀嘛，浑身都是洞</font></font></font>

413
00:25:37,667 --> 00:25:39,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么意思嘛？</font></font></font>

414
00:25:49,042 --> 00:25:51,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师姐，怎么突然不辞而别</font></font></font>

415
00:25:51,833 --> 00:25:53,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">跑到这种穷乡僻壤的地方？</font></font></font>

416
00:25:53,625 --> 00:25:54,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还被一群老粗</font></font></font>

417
00:25:54,917 --> 00:25:57,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">用迷药把你弄得原形毕露</font></font></font>

418
00:25:57,625 --> 00:25:58,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你来干什么？</font></font></font>

419
00:25:58,458 --> 00:25:59,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你呢？</font></font></font>

420
00:25:59,542 --> 00:26:00,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我想出来散散心</font></font></font>

421
00:26:02,333 --> 00:26:04,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你想在这里等唐三藏出现</font></font></font>

422
00:26:04,167 --> 00:26:05,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">尝佢长生不老之肉</font></font></font>

423
00:26:06,792 --> 00:26:08,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你能从菩提老祖口中</font></font></font>

424
00:26:08,375 --> 00:26:09,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">骗他说出这个天机</font></font></font>

425
00:26:09,583 --> 00:26:10,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">难道我就不能吗？</font></font></font>

426
00:26:10,667 --> 00:26:11,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">胡说！</font></font></font>

427
00:26:11,792 --> 00:26:14,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">胡说？那么你跑到五岳山来干什么？</font></font></font>

428
00:26:14,500 --> 00:26:16,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这里以前叫做五指山</font></font></font>

429
00:26:17,208 --> 00:26:18,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是那只死猴子当年被困之地</font></font></font>

430
00:26:18,833 --> 00:26:20,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">天机泄漏他会转世为人</font></font></font>

431
00:26:20,708 --> 00:26:22,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在投胎之后脚底板会有三颗痣</font></font></font>

432
00:26:23,583 --> 00:26:25,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">只要找到他就可以找到唐三藏</font></font></font>

433
00:26:25,833 --> 00:26:28,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师姐，我这么说不知道算在胡说吗？</font></font></font>

434
00:26:29,167 --> 00:26:31,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是你想再看那只臭猴子吧</font></font></font>

435
00:26:32,208 --> 00:26:34,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">再看到那无情无义的人怎么样</font></font></font>

436
00:26:35,250 --> 00:26:37,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不同的是他上次死在观世音手上</font></font></font>

437
00:26:38,750 --> 00:26:40,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这一次却会死在我手上</font></font></font>

438
00:26:41,000 --> 00:26:42,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一个和尚有水喝</font></font></font>

439
00:26:42,708 --> 00:26:44,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">两个和尚没水喝</font></font></font>

440
00:26:44,458 --> 00:26:45,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个道理你都不懂？</font></font></font>

441
00:26:47,500 --> 00:26:48,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">想跟我争</font></font></font>

442
00:26:51,792 --> 00:26:53,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你以为只有你会变？</font></font></font>

443
00:26:56,875 --> 00:26:57,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁？</font></font></font>

444
00:27:06,750 --> 00:27:09,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">妖怪…！</font></font></font>

445
00:27:19,958 --> 00:27:21,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你看到什么？</font></font></font>

446
00:27:21,125 --> 00:27:22,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没什么</font></font></font>

447
00:27:22,083 --> 00:27:22,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没有！</font></font></font>

448
00:27:22,708 --> 00:27:23,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那你蹲下来干什么？</font></font></font>

449
00:27:24,375 --> 00:27:25,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我结鞋带</font></font></font>

450
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:36,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果唐僧这个消息传出去了</font></font></font>

451
00:27:36,708 --> 00:27:38,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我第一个就把你给杀了</font></font></font>

452
00:27:40,292 --> 00:27:42,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">到时候群妖会合五指山</font></font></font>

453
00:27:42,333 --> 00:27:44,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">向师姐讨块唐僧肉吃就行吧！</font></font></font>

454
00:27:44,083 --> 00:27:47,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把唐三藏这个消息报告比大王</font></font></font>

455
00:27:47,167 --> 00:27:48,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一定重重有赏</font></font></font>

456
00:27:53,583 --> 00:27:56,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">连牛都开口说话，这次真是百妖交集</font></font></font>

457
00:27:56,875 --> 00:27:58,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">赶快走…</font></font></font>

458
00:27:59,750 --> 00:28:01,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这样走太不讲义气了！</font></font></font>

459
00:28:01,958 --> 00:28:03,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对！报告帮主</font></font></font>

460
00:28:05,000 --> 00:28:06,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主</font></font></font>

461
00:28:06,125 --> 00:28:07,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">原来我们这里五岳山</font></font></font>

462
00:28:07,542 --> 00:28:09,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就是以前的五指山</font></font></font>

463
00:28:09,083 --> 00:28:11,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">唐僧跟孙悟空在这儿会合</font></font></font>

464
00:28:11,208 --> 00:28:14,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们牛栏的牛居然开口说话了</font></font></font>

465
00:28:14,167 --> 00:28:14,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这两个家伙</font></font></font>

466
00:28:15,042 --> 00:28:17,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一个有八只手，一个的头头头…</font></font></font>

467
00:28:18,250 --> 00:28:19,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">两位还没睡啊？</font></font></font>

468
00:28:20,500 --> 00:28:21,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你在说什么？</font></font></font>

469
00:28:25,708 --> 00:28:26,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没什么</font></font></font>

470
00:28:26,917 --> 00:28:29,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们猪栏的母猪生了两只小猪</font></font></font>

471
00:28:29,333 --> 00:28:31,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一只呢有八…八只脚</font></font></font>

472
00:28:31,417 --> 00:28:33,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">另外一只的头有四百多斤重</font></font></font>

473
00:28:33,917 --> 00:28:35,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主，这一次我们发了</font></font></font>

474
00:28:35,667 --> 00:28:36,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们以后不要再做贼了</font></font></font>

475
00:28:36,875 --> 00:28:38,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们哪有养猪啊？</font></font></font>

476
00:28:38,292 --> 00:28:39,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们没有养猪吗？</font></font></font>

477
00:28:39,667 --> 00:28:42,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">也许我在做梦，我瞎掰的</font></font></font>

478
00:28:42,125 --> 00:28:43,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我走了！我不打扰你们休息了</font></font></font>

479
00:28:44,000 --> 00:28:44,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们也走了</font></font></font>

480
00:28:45,667 --> 00:28:46,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">顺便送两位姑娘出去</font></font></font>

481
00:28:46,875 --> 00:28:47,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不行！</font></font></font>

482
00:28:47,750 --> 00:28:49,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">两位，明天我一定派相关人等</font></font></font>

483
00:28:49,875 --> 00:28:52,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在这里附近彻底搜查你们要找的人</font></font></font>

484
00:28:53,250 --> 00:28:54,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谢谢帮主</font></font></font>

485
00:28:55,250 --> 00:28:57,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主晚安！走啦</font></font></font>

486
00:28:58,917 --> 00:29:00,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">去！去！</font></font></font>

487
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:04,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这下没搞头了</font></font></font>

488
00:29:05,250 --> 00:29:06,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为什么晶晶姑娘对我这个造型</font></font></font>

489
00:29:06,875 --> 00:29:08,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">完全没反应呢？</font></font></font>

490
00:29:09,792 --> 00:29:10,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没办法</font></font></font>

491
00:29:15,458 --> 00:29:16,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走！</font></font></font>

492
00:29:23,542 --> 00:29:27,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要杀我！…不要杀我！</font></font></font>

493
00:29:30,792 --> 00:29:31,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我跟你们玩玩的</font></font></font>

494
00:29:32,333 --> 00:29:33,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">喜欢玩是吧？</font></font></font>

495
00:29:33,792 --> 00:29:34,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们就玩吧！</font></font></font>

496
00:29:39,000 --> 00:29:40,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好不好玩呀？</font></font></font>

497
00:29:40,167 --> 00:29:41,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好玩</font></font></font>

498
00:29:41,167 --> 00:29:42,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好玩再玩一次</font></font></font>

499
00:29:50,875 --> 00:29:51,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还玩不玩呀？</font></font></font>

500
00:29:51,917 --> 00:29:53,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不玩啦…</font></font></font>

501
00:29:54,000 --> 00:29:55,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">刚刚谁说看到有八只爪啊？</font></font></font>

502
00:29:56,000 --> 00:29:57,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不记得了…</font></font></font>

503
00:29:57,250 --> 00:29:58,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">干嘛？</font></font></font>

504
00:30:01,625 --> 00:30:02,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要啊！</font></font></font>

505
00:30:02,958 --> 00:30:04,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我的头是不是这样子的？</font></font></font>

506
00:30:04,958 --> 00:30:06,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是呀，是呀！</font></font></font>

507
00:30:07,500 --> 00:30:09,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是什么嘛？她还没有变</font></font></font>

508
00:30:13,625 --> 00:30:15,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这还没变</font></font></font>

509
00:30:18,500 --> 00:30:19,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一刀杀了他</font></font></font>

510
00:30:19,417 --> 00:30:20,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不行</font></font></font>

511
00:30:21,250 --> 00:30:22,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为什么？</font></font></font>

512
00:30:23,042 --> 00:30:24,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我要用移魂大法迷住他</font></font></font>

513
00:30:24,917 --> 00:30:26,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">留他来做我的卧底</font></font></font>

514
00:30:31,917 --> 00:30:32,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">嗨！</font></font></font>

515
00:30:32,625 --> 00:30:33,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">鬼呀！</font></font></font>

516
00:30:35,000 --> 00:30:35,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">过去看看</font></font></font>

517
00:30:36,833 --> 00:30:38,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这么英雄潚洒你说有鬼！</font></font></font>

518
00:30:38,750 --> 00:30:40,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真是没见过世面</font></font></font>

519
00:30:42,167 --> 00:30:43,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">喏！老大不小的，还给我装蒜</font></font></font>

520
00:30:43,917 --> 00:30:46,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">等一下我一块肉一块肉的给你割下来</font></font></font>

521
00:30:48,000 --> 00:30:49,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不会那么残忍吧？</font></font></font>

522
00:30:49,125 --> 00:30:50,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看着我</font></font></font>

523
00:30:50,375 --> 00:30:51,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">移魂大法</font></font></font>

524
00:31:00,625 --> 00:31:01,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么人？</font></font></font>

525
00:31:02,750 --> 00:31:04,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">长夜漫漫，无心睡眠</font></font></font>

526
00:31:05,125 --> 00:31:06,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我以为只有我睡不着觉</font></font></font>

527
00:31:06,792 --> 00:31:08,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">原来晶晶姑娘你也睡不着啊？</font></font></font>

528
00:31:13,458 --> 00:31:16,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是呀！不知道帮主为什么睡不着？</font></font></font>

529
00:31:16,958 --> 00:31:18,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就系因为晶晶姑娘你</font></font></font>

530
00:31:19,792 --> 00:31:20,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我？</font></font></font>

531
00:31:21,292 --> 00:31:23,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没错！自从看到晶晶姑娘之后</font></font></font>

532
00:31:24,167 --> 00:31:26,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我决定改过自新，不再做贼</font></font></font>

533
00:31:26,417 --> 00:31:28,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为了表示对姑娘你的诚意</font></font></font>

534
00:31:28,500 --> 00:31:30,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不要再看见以前的我</font></font></font>

535
00:31:32,667 --> 00:31:33,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好看吗？</font></font></font>

536
00:31:35,292 --> 00:31:36,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是你这臭猴子？</font></font></font>

537
00:31:37,292 --> 00:31:38,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">臭猴子？</font></font></font>

538
00:31:38,292 --> 00:31:39,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孙悟空</font></font></font>

539
00:31:39,375 --> 00:31:40,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孙悟空？</font></font></font>

540
00:31:40,458 --> 00:31:41,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你变成人样就行了吗？</font></font></font>

541
00:31:41,500 --> 00:31:42,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">人样？</font></font></font>

542
00:31:42,708 --> 00:31:44,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看来我用三味白骨火，你是不会承认</font></font></font>

543
00:31:45,917 --> 00:31:47,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哗！还用得着！又烧！</font></font></font>

544
00:31:48,500 --> 00:31:50,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">何必呢？</font></font></font>

545
00:31:50,917 --> 00:31:51,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">难道我搞错了？</font></font></font>

546
00:31:52,333 --> 00:31:54,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">何必呢？</font></font></font>

547
00:31:57,000 --> 00:31:58,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你干嘛用火焰来烧我？</font></font></font>

548
00:31:58,625 --> 00:32:00,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你把胡子剃光干什么？</font></font></font>

549
00:32:00,500 --> 00:32:01,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你知不知道你少了胡</font></font></font>

550
00:32:01,708 --> 00:32:02,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一点性格都没有啦？</font></font></font>

551
00:32:02,708 --> 00:32:03,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是吗？</font></font></font>

552
00:32:03,625 --> 00:32:05,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">文也不行，武也不行</font></font></font>

553
00:32:05,833 --> 00:32:07,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不做山贼，你想做状元吗</font></font></font>

554
00:32:08,000 --> 00:32:09,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我想过啊，不过</font></font></font>

555
00:32:09,292 --> 00:32:11,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">省省吧你，改变什么形象</font></font></font>

556
00:32:11,167 --> 00:32:13,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好好的做你山贼这份很有前途</font></font></font>

557
00:32:13,083 --> 00:32:14,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">的职业嘛</font></font></font>

558
00:32:15,000 --> 00:32:16,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道了</font></font></font>

559
00:32:16,125 --> 00:32:17,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我一定会继续努力的</font></font></font>

560
00:32:17,833 --> 00:32:19,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么不好像，像个臭猴子</font></font></font>

561
00:32:21,750 --> 00:32:22,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真失败</font></font></font>

562
00:32:23,333 --> 00:32:25,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">原来晶晶姑娘喜欢我粗犷的一面</font></font></font>

563
00:32:31,875 --> 00:32:35,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">乱是乱了点，总算回复了几分风采</font></font></font>

564
00:32:52,500 --> 00:32:53,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孙悟空，你给我滚出来</font></font></font>

565
00:32:54,875 --> 00:32:56,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你个臭猴子</font></font></font>

566
00:32:56,167 --> 00:32:58,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我十八岁那年你说会来娶我</font></font></font>

567
00:32:58,417 --> 00:32:59,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">害我把他等了三年</font></font></font>

568
00:32:59,667 --> 00:33:00,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你给我滚出来</font></font></font>

569
00:33:01,458 --> 00:33:03,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们大王有事出去了</font></font></font>

570
00:33:03,375 --> 00:33:06,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他说白姑娘的话，把这东西还给她</font></font></font>

571
00:33:06,542 --> 00:33:08,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还说感谢白姑娘的美意</font></font></font>

572
00:33:08,708 --> 00:33:09,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他就无福消受了</font></font></font>

573
00:33:19,917 --> 00:33:22,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">五百年了…</font></font></font>

574
00:33:22,292 --> 00:33:24,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我终于找到唐三藏的踪迹了</font></font></font>

575
00:33:32,000 --> 00:33:33,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">连脚底板的毛也剃光了</font></font></font>

576
00:33:33,500 --> 00:33:35,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不知道要那一年才长得出来</font></font></font>

577
00:33:45,083 --> 00:33:48,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">糟了！被那两个家伙先到一步！</font></font></font>

578
00:33:49,083 --> 00:33:51,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我菩提老祖一定要想个办法通知</font></font></font>

579
00:33:51,083 --> 00:33:52,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这群无辜的人</font></font></font>

580
00:34:14,958 --> 00:34:16,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你又回水濂洞来啦？</font></font></font>

581
00:34:17,167 --> 00:34:18,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么？水濂洞？</font></font></font>

582
00:34:18,792 --> 00:34:19,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你是谁你？</font></font></font>

583
00:34:19,958 --> 00:34:21,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么老是带我来这里干嘛？</font></font></font>

584
00:34:21,917 --> 00:34:24,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没有人带你来，是你自己要回来</font></font></font>

585
00:34:25,125 --> 00:34:28,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一个人离开家太久了，总是想回家</font></font></font>

586
00:34:30,500 --> 00:34:31,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不要耍我</font></font></font>

587
00:34:32,000 --> 00:34:35,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我的家在五岳山第四边101号B1</font></font></font>

588
00:34:35,292 --> 00:34:37,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你搞错啦，你听到没有？</font></font></font>

589
00:34:37,208 --> 00:34:39,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">以后不要再烦我啦，拜托！</font></font></font>

590
00:34:42,667 --> 00:34:45,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">出发了帮主，不然会迟到啦</font></font></font>

591
00:34:45,250 --> 00:34:46,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">出什么发啊？</font></font></font>

592
00:34:46,375 --> 00:34:47,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">抢劫呀，帮主</font></font></font>

593
00:34:47,708 --> 00:34:48,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁敢跑来抢劫啊？</font></font></font>

594
00:34:48,708 --> 00:34:49,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们去抢劫人家啦</font></font></font>

595
00:34:49,875 --> 00:34:51,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我知道啦！出发！</font></font></font>

596
00:34:56,083 --> 00:35:00,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">抢劫啊…</font></font></font>

597
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:03,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">抢劫什么？</font></font></font>

598
00:35:03,958 --> 00:35:04,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">脚底板啊，老爷</font></font></font>

599
00:35:04,667 --> 00:35:06,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我没有脚啊，怎么办啊？</font></font></font>

600
00:35:12,417 --> 00:35:13,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看什么看？</font></font></font>

601
00:35:13,583 --> 00:35:15,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">嘴刮干净就英俊多啦，妒忌呀？</font></font></font>

602
00:35:16,125 --> 00:35:17,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">干干净净很好啊</font></font></font>

603
00:35:17,708 --> 00:35:18,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是啊…</font></font></font>

604
00:35:18,792 --> 00:35:19,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">妒忌就妒忌嘛！</font></font></font>

605
00:35:20,000 --> 00:35:21,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还嘴硬！</font></font></font>

606
00:35:24,458 --> 00:35:25,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">葡萄？</font></font></font>

607
00:35:31,458 --> 00:35:33,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主，葡萄已经洗干净了</font></font></font>

608
00:35:33,292 --> 00:35:34,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">出去</font></font></font>

609
00:35:34,125 --> 00:35:34,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晚饭已经准备好了</font></font></font>

610
00:35:34,917 --> 00:35:35,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">出去</font></font></font>

611
00:35:39,042 --> 00:35:40,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁啊？</font></font></font>

612
00:35:42,750 --> 00:35:44,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就是你带回来的那串葡萄</font></font></font>

613
00:35:46,292 --> 00:35:47,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你就是葡萄？</font></font></font>

614
00:35:48,708 --> 00:35:50,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不是！我系菩提老祖</font></font></font>

615
00:35:51,250 --> 00:35:52,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么菩你老母？</font></font></font>

616
00:35:53,208 --> 00:35:54,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你占我便宜</font></font></font>

617
00:35:54,458 --> 00:35:55,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是菩提老祖，我是神仙</font></font></font>

618
00:35:55,875 --> 00:35:57,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我化为葡萄来救你的</font></font></font>

619
00:35:58,750 --> 00:36:01,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你偷了我的葡萄，还菩我老母？</font></font></font>

620
00:36:02,125 --> 00:36:04,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那两个女人是妖怪</font></font></font>

621
00:36:04,958 --> 00:36:05,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果你不相信</font></font></font>

622
00:36:05,917 --> 00:36:07,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我的照妖镜一照，你就会明白了</font></font></font>

623
00:36:07,500 --> 00:36:10,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我照你老母的妖镜</font></font></font>

624
00:36:10,333 --> 00:36:11,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你是不是偷了我葡萄？</font></font></font>

625
00:36:11,667 --> 00:36:12,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我没有啊！</font></font></font>

626
00:36:13,042 --> 00:36:14,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没有？那我的葡萄到那儿去了？</font></font></font>

627
00:36:14,458 --> 00:36:16,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就是葡萄了！</font></font></font>

628
00:36:16,167 --> 00:36:17,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大声点</font></font></font>

629
00:36:17,500 --> 00:36:18,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就是你的葡萄</font></font></font>

630
00:36:18,917 --> 00:36:22,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为什么不做苹果？要做葡萄</font></font></font>

631
00:36:23,208 --> 00:36:24,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你别以为我打不过你</font></font></font>

632
00:36:24,917 --> 00:36:26,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我只是不想伤及无辜</font></font></font>

633
00:36:26,375 --> 00:36:27,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">来呀！</font></font></font>

634
00:36:27,500 --> 00:36:28,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我打你这个老糊涂</font></font></font>

635
00:36:31,833 --> 00:36:32,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶姑娘</font></font></font>

636
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:34,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你的胡子好粗犷呀</font></font></font>

637
00:36:34,375 --> 00:36:35,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是吗？</font></font></font>

638
00:36:35,958 --> 00:36:37,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">乒拎乓啷的是什么声音？</font></font></font>

639
00:36:37,417 --> 00:36:39,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我刚刚在打一串葡萄</font></font></font>

640
00:36:42,083 --> 00:36:44,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那里会有人打葡萄的？</font></font></font>

641
00:36:44,958 --> 00:36:45,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">吃饭吧</font></font></font>

642
00:36:47,333 --> 00:36:48,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">吃饭了</font></font></font>

643
00:36:48,417 --> 00:36:49,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">吃饭好啊</font></font></font>

644
00:36:49,667 --> 00:36:50,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好是吗？</font></font></font>

645
00:36:51,375 --> 00:36:53,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我看今天月亮这么美，不如…</font></font></font>

646
00:36:53,250 --> 00:36:54,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">月光？没有啊？</font></font></font>

647
00:36:56,125 --> 00:36:58,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那么大的月亮你没看到吗？看清楚点</font></font></font>

648
00:36:59,375 --> 00:37:02,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">天还没有黑，那来的月光</font></font></font>

649
00:37:02,250 --> 00:37:03,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说啊…</font></font></font>

650
00:37:08,292 --> 00:37:09,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哎菩什么老母？</font></font></font>

651
00:37:09,583 --> 00:37:10,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">菩什么老母？</font></font></font>

652
00:37:10,583 --> 00:37:11,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我变成葡萄了</font></font></font>

653
00:37:11,833 --> 00:37:12,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你在哪里啊？</font></font></font>

654
00:37:12,833 --> 00:37:13,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我在你的裤裆里面</font></font></font>

655
00:37:15,208 --> 00:37:16,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哗！这么大一串？</font></font></font>

656
00:37:16,625 --> 00:37:18,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那串是你的，我在你后面</font></font></font>

657
00:37:19,417 --> 00:37:20,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">再见到你太好了</font></font></font>

658
00:37:20,667 --> 00:37:21,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你现在相信啦！</font></font></font>

659
00:37:21,667 --> 00:37:22,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我相信了，相信了</font></font></font>

660
00:37:24,000 --> 00:37:25,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我这里怎么会有妖怪出现啊？</font></font></font>

661
00:37:26,333 --> 00:37:28,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">笨蛋啊，我告诉你吧！</font></font></font>

662
00:37:29,042 --> 00:37:33,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这群妖怪呢是等唐三藏重现人间</font></font></font>

663
00:37:33,583 --> 00:37:35,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">唐三藏重现人间？</font></font></font>

664
00:37:37,750 --> 00:37:41,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">五百年前孙悟空被观音大使所消灭</font></font></font>

665
00:37:41,708 --> 00:37:43,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他师父唐三藏为了救他</font></font></font>

666
00:37:43,667 --> 00:37:44,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">用自己的性命</font></font></font>

667
00:37:44,917 --> 00:37:46,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">换取孙悟空一次重生的机会</font></font></font>

668
00:37:46,875 --> 00:37:48,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">希望这只猴子能改邪归正</font></font></font>

669
00:37:49,333 --> 00:37:50,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">唐三藏为什么在这里出现</font></font></font>

670
00:37:50,833 --> 00:37:52,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你还没告诉我？</font></font></font>

671
00:37:53,500 --> 00:37:56,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不错！唐三藏当年为了普渡众生</font></font></font>

672
00:37:56,750 --> 00:37:58,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不怕千辛万苦去取西经</font></font></font>

673
00:37:58,875 --> 00:38:01,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">希望藉此经书来感化世人</font></font></font>

674
00:38:01,625 --> 00:38:04,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">满天神佛都被他这种精神所感动</font></font></font>

675
00:38:05,292 --> 00:38:06,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">玉皇大帝眼见如此</font></font></font>

676
00:38:06,875 --> 00:38:08,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">因此给孙悟空一个机会转世</font></font></font>

677
00:38:08,875 --> 00:38:11,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">安排他们师徒今世在这里重逢</font></font></font>

678
00:38:11,250 --> 00:38:13,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">继续去完成取西经的使命</font></font></font>

679
00:38:14,625 --> 00:38:16,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为什么那么多妖在这儿出现</font></font></font>

680
00:38:16,792 --> 00:38:17,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你明白了</font></font></font>

681
00:38:19,917 --> 00:38:21,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怪不得我长久以来都在做同样的</font></font></font>

682
00:38:21,125 --> 00:38:22,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一个恶梦</font></font></font>

683
00:38:23,208 --> 00:38:26,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在一遍漆黑孤独的环境里头</font></font></font>

684
00:38:26,958 --> 00:38:29,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一对一对非常迷迷的眼睛</font></font></font>

685
00:38:29,750 --> 00:38:30,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一直盯着我看</font></font></font>

686
00:38:31,542 --> 00:38:33,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看得我都非常不好意思</font></font></font>

687
00:38:33,542 --> 00:38:34,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就是你这种眼神</font></font></font>

688
00:38:34,875 --> 00:38:36,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有好几次盯得我脸都红了</font></font></font>

689
00:38:37,625 --> 00:38:39,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">原来注定我今天撞妖！</font></font></font>

690
00:38:39,458 --> 00:38:42,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对呀！你今天真是撞妖了</font></font></font>

691
00:38:42,292 --> 00:38:44,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这两个乾坤袋，一迭隐身符</font></font></font>

692
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:47,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你把符贴在身上，她们就看不到你了</font></font></font>

693
00:38:47,458 --> 00:38:49,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">趁她们不注意，你就套在他们头上</font></font></font>

694
00:38:49,917 --> 00:38:51,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">去吧！我在后面掩护你</font></font></font>

695
00:38:51,792 --> 00:38:53,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你这句对白一直都是我说的</font></font></font>

696
00:38:53,667 --> 00:38:55,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你跟谁说的？</font></font></font>

697
00:38:55,083 --> 00:38:56,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">跟他</font></font></font>

698
00:38:57,125 --> 00:39:00,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对啊！我当然帮你</font></font></font>

699
00:39:00,125 --> 00:39:02,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">了不起！不愧是我的好哥们</font></font></font>

700
00:39:02,417 --> 00:39:03,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你现在出去叫所有兄弟进来</font></font></font>

701
00:39:03,792 --> 00:39:05,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">每个人给一道符</font></font></font>

702
00:39:05,125 --> 00:39:06,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我回菩提老祖那儿拿乾坤袋来</font></font></font>

703
00:39:06,917 --> 00:39:08,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们一起抓妖怪</font></font></font>

704
00:39:08,375 --> 00:39:09,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没问题</font></font></font>

705
00:39:09,500 --> 00:39:10,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好哥们</font></font></font>

706
00:39:13,125 --> 00:39:14,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你今天的眼神这么…</font></font></font>

707
00:39:14,458 --> 00:39:15,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">淫荡吗？</font></font></font>

708
00:39:15,292 --> 00:39:16,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对啊</font></font></font>

709
00:39:20,708 --> 00:39:22,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我一定帮你的</font></font></font>

710
00:39:36,958 --> 00:39:38,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">两位，请慢用</font></font></font>

711
00:39:38,833 --> 00:39:39,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么办？</font></font></font>

712
00:39:40,042 --> 00:39:41,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有什么办法，是帮主吩咐的</font></font></font>

713
00:39:41,958 --> 00:39:43,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那你也得想个办法</font></font></font>

714
00:39:44,000 --> 00:39:44,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">二当家</font></font></font>

715
00:39:48,083 --> 00:39:49,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">通知其它人，帮主找我们</font></font></font>

716
00:39:49,625 --> 00:39:50,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快去…</font></font></font>

717
00:39:57,125 --> 00:39:58,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">隐身符</font></font></font>

718
00:39:59,667 --> 00:40:01,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走吧…</font></font></font>

719
00:40:05,958 --> 00:40:06,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师姐</font></font></font>

720
00:40:06,875 --> 00:40:07,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">知道了…</font></font></font>

721
00:40:07,833 --> 00:40:09,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们不动声色，看看他们想干什么</font></font></font>

722
00:40:22,333 --> 00:40:24,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师妹，喝酒呀！</font></font></font>

723
00:40:39,083 --> 00:40:40,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师姐，你也喝</font></font></font>

724
00:40:47,292 --> 00:40:48,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你怎么啦？</font></font></font>

725
00:40:49,208 --> 00:40:51,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我有点醉，我想睡一下</font></font></font>

726
00:40:52,125 --> 00:40:54,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不用怕，看不到的</font></font></font>

727
00:40:54,083 --> 00:40:55,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不能喝就别喝嘛，真是丢人</font></font></font>

728
00:41:17,375 --> 00:41:18,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真的看不到</font></font></font>

729
00:41:18,708 --> 00:41:20,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你本来就看不到</font></font></font>

730
00:41:20,083 --> 00:41:20,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走</font></font></font>

731
00:41:25,583 --> 00:41:27,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怪了，帮主怎么还没来</font></font></font>

732
00:41:27,167 --> 00:41:28,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就是</font></font></font>

733
00:41:28,292 --> 00:41:29,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不是说有烤鸡嘛？</font></font></font>

734
00:41:39,792 --> 00:41:41,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主！着火啦</font></font></font>

735
00:41:43,292 --> 00:41:44,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不能脱</font></font></font>

736
00:42:34,042 --> 00:42:35,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快还钱啊，混蛋！</font></font></font>

737
00:42:35,375 --> 00:42:36,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说就说，干什么那么凶呀？</font></font></font>

738
00:42:36,917 --> 00:42:38,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我凶不行啊？借了钱不用还哪？</font></font></font>

739
00:42:38,333 --> 00:42:39,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你放屁，我什么时候跟你借了</font></font></font>

740
00:42:39,750 --> 00:42:40,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是你欠我钱呀？</font></font></font>

741
00:42:41,083 --> 00:42:42,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我欠你？</font></font></font>

742
00:42:42,083 --> 00:42:43,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么？不记得了吧？</font></font></font>

743
00:42:43,625 --> 00:42:44,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对啊！</font></font></font>

744
00:42:44,750 --> 00:42:46,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没记性</font></font></font>

745
00:42:46,208 --> 00:42:48,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对不起</font></font></font>

746
00:43:09,458 --> 00:43:11,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">妈的！现在该你还钱</font></font></font>

747
00:43:11,167 --> 00:43:12,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">喂！你用得着那么凶吗？</font></font></font>

748
00:43:12,292 --> 00:43:13,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不还钱我毁你容啊！</font></font></font>

749
00:43:13,875 --> 00:43:15,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我上个月不是已经还你了吗？</font></font></font>

750
00:43:15,333 --> 00:43:18,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还了？对对对已经还了！</font></font></font>

751
00:43:18,292 --> 00:43:20,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你老了，记忆力衰退了</font></font></font>

752
00:43:21,458 --> 00:43:23,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">算了，刚刚是我先不对嘛</font></font></font>

753
00:43:25,167 --> 00:43:27,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">割了吧！都烧焦了</font></font></font>

754
00:43:28,000 --> 00:43:30,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">脆了点！总比没有好</font></font></font>

755
00:43:30,833 --> 00:43:32,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">明刀明枪跟他们拚了</font></font></font>

756
00:43:32,292 --> 00:43:33,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">兄弟们，现身</font></font></font>

757
00:43:33,417 --> 00:43:34,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是</font></font></font>

758
00:43:37,750 --> 00:43:39,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">两只妖怪，出来受死吧！</font></font></font>

759
00:43:42,250 --> 00:43:43,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我的乾坤袋到哪里去了？</font></font></font>

760
00:43:44,167 --> 00:43:46,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">乾坤袋在这里，主人，他们想害你</font></font></font>

761
00:43:48,208 --> 00:43:49,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">吃里扒外，你出卖我们？</font></font></font>

762
00:43:54,292 --> 00:43:55,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不过他今天能出卖我</font></font></font>

763
00:43:55,750 --> 00:43:57,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">明天也能够出卖你们</font></font></font>

764
00:43:57,542 --> 00:43:58,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是吗？</font></font></font>

765
00:43:58,875 --> 00:44:00,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是啊！</font></font></font>

766
00:44:03,792 --> 00:44:05,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我菩提老祖为了伏妖除魔</font></font></font>

767
00:44:05,542 --> 00:44:07,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">三角裤都脱了</font></font></font>

768
00:44:11,292 --> 00:44:14,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主果然有眼光，二当家真的有问题</font></font></font>

769
