<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这老小子平常叫他做事，推三阻四</font></font></font>

770
00:44:16,708 --> 00:44:18,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今次这么爽快，一定有问题</font></font></font>

771
00:44:18,917 --> 00:44:19,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把他拖出来</font></font></font>

772
00:44:19,875 --> 00:44:20,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是！</font></font></font>

773
00:44:21,917 --> 00:44:23,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">放开我</font></font></font>

774
00:44:23,792 --> 00:44:24,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">放开我</font></font></font>

775
00:44:25,500 --> 00:44:26,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">少啰嗦</font></font></font>

776
00:44:26,708 --> 00:44:27,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">放开我…</font></font></font>

777
00:44:29,417 --> 00:44:30,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">跪下</font></font></font>

778
00:44:30,875 --> 00:44:34,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你这叛徒，今天晚上把你杀了烤来吃</font></font></font>

779
00:44:34,875 --> 00:44:35,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好！</font></font></font>

780
00:44:36,417 --> 00:44:38,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个也不能怪他</font></font></font>

781
00:44:38,125 --> 00:44:40,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他只不过是中了两个妖女的移魂大法</font></font></font>

782
00:44:41,917 --> 00:44:42,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">放了我！</font></font></font>

783
00:44:43,042 --> 00:44:44,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不然我叫我主人杀了你们</font></font></font>

784
00:44:44,667 --> 00:44:45,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你还敢多！</font></font></font>

785
00:44:48,417 --> 00:44:49,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">旺财</font></font></font>

786
00:44:49,917 --> 00:44:52,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你咬着的绳子我怎么觉得好面熟啊？</font></font></font>

787
00:44:52,958 --> 00:44:55,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">就是我绑乾坤袋条的绳子</font></font></font>

788
00:45:01,208 --> 00:45:03,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">天堂有路你不走，地狱无门你闯进来</font></font></font>

789
00:45:04,625 --> 00:45:05,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">来吧！</font></font></font>

790
00:45:05,917 --> 00:45:07,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">让我掐死你个托世孙悟空</font></font></font>

791
00:45:07,625 --> 00:45:09,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你就永远都找不到唐三藏了</font></font></font>

792
00:45:10,625 --> 00:45:11,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么？</font></font></font>

793
00:45:11,667 --> 00:45:12,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他是孙悟空？</font></font></font>

794
00:45:14,083 --> 00:45:15,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你要暂时冒充啊</font></font></font>

795
00:45:15,667 --> 00:45:17,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不然我们就完蛋去了</font></font></font>

796
00:45:17,458 --> 00:45:18,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他不是孙悟空</font></font></font>

797
00:45:18,667 --> 00:45:20,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他连我三味白骨火都受不了</font></font></font>

798
00:45:20,333 --> 00:45:21,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么会是孙悟空呢？</font></font></font>

799
00:45:21,542 --> 00:45:22,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">玩笑开大了吧？</font></font></font>

800
00:45:22,625 --> 00:45:24,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这种天机你也敢泄露出来？</font></font></font>

801
00:45:25,125 --> 00:45:26,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这一边</font></font></font>

802
00:45:26,750 --> 00:45:28,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你算是个神仙吗你</font></font></font>

803
00:45:28,458 --> 00:45:29,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把手拿过来</font></font></font>

804
00:45:30,167 --> 00:45:31,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">过份…</font></font></font>

805
00:45:32,708 --> 00:45:34,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你以为我真的怕你的三味白骨火吗？</font></font></font>

806
00:45:34,708 --> 00:45:35,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你再烧一次试试看</font></font></font>

807
00:45:36,333 --> 00:45:37,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">来真的？</font></font></font>

808
00:45:37,625 --> 00:45:38,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好！</font></font></font>

809
00:45:41,125 --> 00:45:43,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不怕啦！对不对？</font></font></font>

810
00:45:43,500 --> 00:45:44,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对啊！</font></font></font>

811
00:45:49,625 --> 00:45:51,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我孙悟空就一直把手放在这里让你烧</font></font></font>

812
00:45:52,792 --> 00:45:54,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">让他们见识，见识！</font></font></font>

813
00:45:55,708 --> 00:45:57,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不就是烧手吗？</font></font></font>

814
00:46:04,708 --> 00:46:05,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">焦了</font></font></font>

815
00:46:08,958 --> 00:46:10,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">真的烧焦了也没有事</font></font></font>

816
00:46:12,375 --> 00:46:13,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">放手！</font></font></font>

817
00:46:14,625 --> 00:46:15,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你现在知道我真的啦</font></font></font>

818
00:46:16,042 --> 00:46:16,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快点投降</font></font></font>

819
00:46:17,042 --> 00:46:19,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我还有一班兄弟，再加上一个神仙</font></font></font>

820
00:46:19,208 --> 00:46:20,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你到哪里去了呀？</font></font></font>

821
00:46:20,375 --> 00:46:21,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我改天帮你报仇</font></font></font>

822
00:46:22,500 --> 00:46:23,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">哗！连神仙都不讲义气</font></font></font>

823
00:46:23,917 --> 00:46:25,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那不用说了</font></font></font>

824
00:46:25,167 --> 00:46:26,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我那帮兄弟一定站到那边去了</font></font></font>

825
00:46:27,667 --> 00:46:29,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是的，帮主！</font></font></font>

826
00:46:29,625 --> 00:46:31,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">唉！一群大白痴</font></font></font>

827
00:46:32,667 --> 00:46:34,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你就是那个负心人？</font></font></font>

828
00:46:34,375 --> 00:46:35,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">昨天晚上骗我！</font></font></font>

829
00:46:37,125 --> 00:46:38,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可恶的臭猴子</font></font></font>

830
00:46:38,667 --> 00:46:40,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我师妹嫁不出去就是因为你</font></font></font>

831
00:46:40,917 --> 00:46:41,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我？</font></font></font>

832
00:46:44,125 --> 00:46:45,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">抓住至尊宝！</font></font></font>

833
00:46:45,208 --> 00:46:46,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">上！</font></font></font>

834
00:46:46,292 --> 00:46:47,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要乱来！</font></font></font>

835
00:46:47,625 --> 00:46:49,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主快跑呀</font></font></font>

836
00:46:58,542 --> 00:46:59,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要杀我的兄弟呀</font></font></font>

837
00:47:22,500 --> 00:47:23,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">帮主</font></font></font>

838
00:47:30,375 --> 00:47:32,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">瞎子，不用怕，有我在</font></font></font>

839
00:47:35,292 --> 00:47:36,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对不起啊，瞎子！</font></font></font>

840
00:47:36,417 --> 00:47:37,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今次算了少走了一步</font></font></font>

841
00:47:37,875 --> 00:47:38,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不会怪我吧？</font></font></font>

842
00:47:39,042 --> 00:47:42,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我一辈子…　﹣我知道</font></font></font>

843
00:47:42,458 --> 00:47:43,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">都是个瞎子</font></font></font>

844
00:47:44,042 --> 00:47:47,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我最有眼光就是跟着帮主</font></font></font>

845
00:47:52,750 --> 00:47:54,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我跟你们拚了</font></font></font>

846
00:47:58,167 --> 00:47:59,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">去死吧你</font></font></font>

847
00:47:59,250 --> 00:48:00,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不能杀这个负心人</font></font></font>

848
00:48:00,333 --> 00:48:01,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你还帮着他</font></font></font>

849
00:48:01,458 --> 00:48:02,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">还要靠他找唐僧的</font></font></font>

850
00:48:03,125 --> 00:48:04,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">带他回盘丝洞</font></font></font>

851
00:48:08,667 --> 00:48:09,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师姐</font></font></font>

852
00:48:10,750 --> 00:48:13,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一个和尚有水喝，两个和尚没水喝</font></font></font>

853
00:48:14,000 --> 00:48:15,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个道理原来你不懂</font></font></font>

854
00:48:16,458 --> 00:48:18,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你打伤我，也不见得一定有水喝</font></font></font>

855
00:48:18,625 --> 00:48:19,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你自己看看手掌</font></font></font>

856
00:48:21,292 --> 00:48:22,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">黑寡妇</font></font></font>

857
00:48:24,458 --> 00:48:26,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你中了我的盘丝软夹毒</font></font></font>

858
00:48:26,083 --> 00:48:27,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">七日之内没有我的解药</font></font></font>

859
00:48:27,542 --> 00:48:28,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你就会毒气攻心而死</font></font></font>

860
00:48:30,000 --> 00:48:32,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师姐，我再也不敢了</font></font></font>

861
00:48:32,167 --> 00:48:33,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">滚开！</font></font></font>

862
00:48:37,167 --> 00:48:39,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">终于良心发现了你</font></font></font>

863
00:48:39,125 --> 00:48:41,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不是啦！外面来了个更狠的</font></font></font>

864
00:48:43,333 --> 00:48:44,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">出去看看</font></font></font>

865
00:48:46,292 --> 00:48:47,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们上哪去？</font></font></font>

866
00:48:47,500 --> 00:48:48,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">别去啊</font></font></font>

867
00:48:52,833 --> 00:48:54,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">牛魔王也来了？</font></font></font>

868
00:48:54,167 --> 00:48:55,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">牛魔王？</font></font></font>

869
00:49:04,000 --> 00:49:04,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你也装死啊？</font></font></font>

870
00:49:05,083 --> 00:49:05,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我也是</font></font></font>

871
00:49:07,833 --> 00:49:08,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怪兽</font></font></font>

872
00:49:20,708 --> 00:49:21,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">菩提老祖</font></font></font>

873
00:49:22,333 --> 00:49:24,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今日不把唐三藏交出来</font></font></font>

874
00:49:24,083 --> 00:49:25,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">死路一条</font></font></font>

875
00:49:25,208 --> 00:49:26,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">少废话！</font></font></font>

876
00:49:26,375 --> 00:49:27,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你问托世孙悟空嘛</font></font></font>

877
00:49:28,458 --> 00:49:29,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我结拜老弟孙悟空？</font></font></font>

878
00:49:30,792 --> 00:49:31,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在哪？</font></font></font>

879
00:49:32,750 --> 00:49:33,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个更凶狠的</font></font></font>

880
00:49:33,792 --> 00:49:35,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">原来是孙悟空的结拜大哥</font></font></font>

881
00:49:35,125 --> 00:49:36,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这次有救了</font></font></font>

882
00:49:36,875 --> 00:49:38,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">小弟就是结拜大哥你的</font></font></font>

883
00:49:38,208 --> 00:49:39,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">结拜弟弟孙悟空托世</font></font></font>

884
00:49:41,375 --> 00:49:42,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是你？</font></font></font>

885
00:49:42,333 --> 00:49:43,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">正是小弟</font></font></font>

886
00:49:44,208 --> 00:49:46,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我杀了你这个勾引二嫂的王八蛋！</font></font></font>

887
00:49:51,083 --> 00:49:52,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">何方妖女！报上名来</font></font></font>

888
00:49:53,458 --> 00:49:55,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">盘丝大仙座下大弟子白骨精，蜘蛛精</font></font></font>

889
00:49:56,333 --> 00:49:58,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我认识你们祖师盘丝大仙的时候</font></font></font>

890
00:49:58,750 --> 00:50:01,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你们两个还不知道在那里？</font></font></font>

891
00:50:02,000 --> 00:50:03,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天居然敢跟我放肆</font></font></font>

892
00:50:03,917 --> 00:50:05,209
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">变…</font></font></font>

893
00:50:09,458 --> 00:50:11,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天有谁敢挡我</font></font></font>

894
00:50:11,875 --> 00:50:12,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就杀了谁</font></font></font>

895
00:50:13,417 --> 00:50:14,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">尝尝我的白骨鞭！</font></font></font>

896
00:50:38,417 --> 00:50:39,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">变</font></font></font>

897
00:50:40,583 --> 00:50:41,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">神龙盘丝</font></font></font>

898
00:50:53,667 --> 00:50:54,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快走！</font></font></font>

899
00:50:55,917 --> 00:50:57,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">雕虫小技</font></font></font>

900
00:51:42,042 --> 00:51:43,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">瞎子，你不是死了吗？</font></font></font>

901
00:51:44,042 --> 00:51:45,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们刚刚是装死的</font></font></font>

902
00:51:46,583 --> 00:51:47,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我服了你</font></font></font>

903
00:51:50,250 --> 00:51:52,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要走呀…</font></font></font>

904
00:51:54,000 --> 00:51:55,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看看你们还有什么法宝？</font></font></font>

905
00:51:56,292 --> 00:51:57,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">死牛魔王　﹣走</font></font></font>

906
00:52:07,750 --> 00:52:08,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他打伤了我菩提根</font></font></font>

907
00:52:08,917 --> 00:52:11,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">起码得练上一百八十年才能跟他们斗</font></font></font>

908
00:52:16,125 --> 00:52:17,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">起床了！</font></font></font>

909
00:52:21,292 --> 00:52:22,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你干什么？</font></font></font>

910
00:52:24,417 --> 00:52:25,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我主人要见你</font></font></font>

911
00:52:27,125 --> 00:52:28,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这是什么地方？</font></font></font>

912
00:52:28,417 --> 00:52:29,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">盘丝洞</font></font></font>

913
00:52:31,458 --> 00:52:32,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">盘丝洞？</font></font></font>

914
00:52:32,542 --> 00:52:33,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">对！</font></font></font>

915
00:52:33,542 --> 00:52:36,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我主人是盘丝大仙座下大弟子蜘蛛精</font></font></font>

916
00:52:36,333 --> 00:52:37,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这里不是盘丝洞是什么？</font></font></font>

917
00:52:38,417 --> 00:52:40,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">盘丝洞？</font></font></font>

918
00:52:40,208 --> 00:52:41,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走吧，臭猴子！</font></font></font>

919
00:52:41,375 --> 00:52:42,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你疯啦</font></font></font>

920
00:52:42,875 --> 00:52:44,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是你的帮主呀，臭猴子！</font></font></font>

921
00:52:44,917 --> 00:52:45,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是疯了</font></font></font>

922
00:52:46,333 --> 00:52:47,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">可是你还在装傻</font></font></font>

923
00:52:47,417 --> 00:52:48,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在山寨已经承认了</font></font></font>

924
00:52:48,458 --> 00:52:49,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">自己是齐天大圣了嘛</font></font></font>

925
00:52:49,958 --> 00:52:50,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走吧</font></font></font>

926
00:52:50,875 --> 00:52:51,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你聪明点</font></font></font>

927
00:52:51,875 --> 00:52:53,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是被逼暂时假装的</font></font></font>

928
00:52:53,125 --> 00:52:54,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不相信你拿个照妖镜看看我是不是？</font></font></font>

929
00:52:56,167 --> 00:52:57,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">照妖境？</font></font></font>

930
00:53:05,125 --> 00:53:06,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看到了吧，看到了没有？</font></font></font>

931
00:53:06,292 --> 00:53:08,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看到了！</font></font></font>

932
00:53:08,250 --> 00:53:09,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">清楚吗？</font></font></font>

933
00:53:11,000 --> 00:53:11,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">骗我！</font></font></font>

934
00:53:11,875 --> 00:53:12,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个根本就不是照妖镜</font></font></font>

935
00:53:14,625 --> 00:53:16,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">猪呀！</font></font></font>

936
00:53:19,042 --> 00:53:20,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师姐，你可怜我吧</font></font></font>

937
00:53:21,583 --> 00:53:22,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你急什么</font></font></font>

938
00:53:22,917 --> 00:53:24,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在这段时间只要你乖乖的听话</font></font></font>

939
00:53:24,125 --> 00:53:25,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我保证你无事</font></font></font>

940
00:53:25,833 --> 00:53:26,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">主人！</font></font></font>

941
00:53:26,958 --> 00:53:28,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">主人呀！</font></font></font>

942
00:53:28,125 --> 00:53:29,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">主人呀！臭猴子来了</font></font></font>

943
00:53:30,500 --> 00:53:33,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">唐三藏究竟在哪里？臭猴子</font></font></font>

944
00:53:35,750 --> 00:53:37,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好大的误会呀</font></font></font>

945
00:53:38,250 --> 00:53:39,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这个误会大到怎样？</font></font></font>

946
00:53:39,333 --> 00:53:40,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我偷偷地跟你们说</font></font></font>

947
00:53:40,417 --> 00:53:42,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我真是属猴，不过其实就不是猴子</font></font></font>

948
00:53:42,917 --> 00:53:43,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不用说了！</font></font></font>

949
00:53:43,917 --> 00:53:45,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我照妖镜又有，什么都有</font></font></font>

950
00:53:45,167 --> 00:53:46,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你用来照照看</font></font></font>

951
00:53:46,125 --> 00:53:46,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">假的，假的</font></font></font>

952
00:53:46,958 --> 00:53:47,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">假的你都也敢…</font></font></font>

953
00:53:47,792 --> 00:53:48,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不要再装蒜呀</font></font></font>

954
00:53:49,958 --> 00:53:51,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">如果我真是孙悟空</font></font></font>

955
00:53:51,292 --> 00:53:52,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就不会被你咬住只手</font></font></font>

956
00:53:52,667 --> 00:53:53,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一个跟斗飞上天</font></font></font>

957
00:53:53,750 --> 00:53:55,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">然后在你们天灵盖拉个屎</font></font></font>

958
00:53:55,667 --> 00:53:56,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你现在没变真身</font></font></font>

959
00:53:56,833 --> 00:53:57,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">到时你以为你不会</font></font></font>

960
00:53:59,917 --> 00:54:00,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么样？师妹</font></font></font>

961
00:54:01,833 --> 00:54:02,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">心痛呀？</font></font></font>

962
00:54:03,625 --> 00:54:04,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不是呀！</font></font></font>

963
00:54:04,625 --> 00:54:05,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不是？</font></font></font>

964
00:54:07,708 --> 00:54:09,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我不会再为这个男人心痛</font></font></font>

965
00:54:11,167 --> 00:54:12,084
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你欺骗我！</font></font></font>

966
00:54:13,875 --> 00:54:14,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师姐，我没有骗你</font></font></font>

967
00:54:16,042 --> 00:54:17,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没有骗我？那你一剑杀了他吧</font></font></font>

968
00:54:19,042 --> 00:54:19,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">杀了他</font></font></font>

969
00:54:20,667 --> 00:54:21,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那你不想找唐三藏吗？</font></font></font>

970
00:54:22,917 --> 00:54:25,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">想呀！但是我不相信你会一剑杀了他</font></font></font>

971
00:54:32,000 --> 00:54:32,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">都不准…</font></font></font>

972
00:54:33,000 --> 00:54:34,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把剑给他！</font></font></font>

973
00:54:36,167 --> 00:54:37,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">给他吧！　﹣知道！</font></font></font>

974
00:54:40,583 --> 00:54:41,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">杀他！</font></font></font>

975
00:54:42,292 --> 00:54:43,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你刺中我大腿呀</font></font></font>

976
00:54:43,667 --> 00:54:44,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是故意的</font></font></font>

977
00:54:44,667 --> 00:54:45,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那你要赔偿我医药费呀？</font></font></font>

978
00:54:46,000 --> 00:54:46,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不用客气</font></font></font>

979
00:54:47,375 --> 00:54:48,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我要杀你！</font></font></font>

980
00:54:51,583 --> 00:54:54,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">贱人，早知道你对臭猴子余情未了</font></font></font>

981
00:54:54,250 --> 00:54:55,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">废话少说，干丢你</font></font></font>

982
00:55:12,875 --> 00:55:13,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没事吗？</font></font></font>

983
00:55:18,958 --> 00:55:21,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在危急时刻仍这样关心我</font></font></font>

984
00:55:22,292 --> 00:55:24,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">从现在开始，爱你一百年</font></font></font>

985
00:55:31,333 --> 00:55:32,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">在外面</font></font></font>

986
00:55:32,292 --> 00:55:33,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这门安全不安全呀？</font></font></font>

987
00:55:33,625 --> 00:55:35,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这门是祖师爷用万年金刚石做的</font></font></font>

988
00:55:39,500 --> 00:55:40,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走开</font></font></font>

989
00:55:43,625 --> 00:55:45,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">师妹，你不记得他以前怎么对你啦？</font></font></font>

990
00:55:46,792 --> 00:55:48,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他欺骗感情，背弃婚约</font></font></font>

991
00:55:48,583 --> 00:55:50,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你原本跟赤炼神君有段美好的姻缘</font></font></font>

992
00:55:50,542 --> 00:55:51,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">都被他搞坏了</font></font></font>

993
00:55:52,417 --> 00:55:53,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">他现在还没本事</font></font></font>

994
00:55:53,500 --> 00:55:54,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">等他回复真身之后</font></font></font>

995
00:55:54,292 --> 00:55:55,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">一样不理你的</font></font></font>

996
00:55:55,333 --> 00:55:56,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你他妈的有完没完啊？</font></font></font>

997
00:55:56,583 --> 00:55:57,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">臭猴子，你敢骂我！</font></font></font>

998
00:55:58,542 --> 00:55:59,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就骂你怎么样？</font></font></font>

999
00:56:00,458 --> 00:56:02,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你别以为躲在里面很安全</font></font></font>

1000
00:56:02,417 --> 00:56:03,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">今天是十五月圆之夜</font></font></font>

1001
00:56:03,833 --> 00:56:05,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">到时候她尸变，你死得难看</font></font></font>

1002
00:56:08,958 --> 00:56:10,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我是吓大的</font></font></font>

1003
00:56:18,208 --> 00:56:19,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么？</font></font></font>

1004
00:56:19,458 --> 00:56:22,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大王，这里有几千个山，山洞又多</font></font></font>

1005
00:56:22,042 --> 00:56:23,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不知道哪个才是盘丝洞的入口？</font></font></font>

1006
00:56:23,542 --> 00:56:24,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是啊…</font></font></font>

1007
00:56:24,917 --> 00:56:28,459
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是吗？比我身上的牛虱还多，给我找</font></font></font>

1008
00:57:00,125 --> 00:57:01,500
