1136
01:06:59,875 --> 01:07:00,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">晶晶</font></font></font>

1137
01:07:01,583 --> 01:07:02,875
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">毒发滚下山咯！</font></font></font>

1138
01:07:05,500 --> 01:07:06,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">讨厌，就是因为你</font></font></font>

1139
01:07:06,708 --> 01:07:08,166
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">为什么让我睡一个晚上？</font></font></font>

1140
01:07:08,208 --> 01:07:09,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不连夜赶来</font></font></font>

1141
01:07:09,292 --> 01:07:10,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你为什么不快马加鞭？</font></font></font>

1142
01:07:10,458 --> 01:07:12,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我一定跟得上</font></font></font>

1143
01:07:12,500 --> 01:07:13,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你别希望我把唐僧的告诉你</font></font></font>

1144
01:07:13,792 --> 01:07:15,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我什么都不知道</font></font></font>

1145
01:07:15,833 --> 01:07:17,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你自己走得慢还怪我？</font></font></font>

1146
01:07:20,875 --> 01:07:21,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么？</font></font></font>

1147
01:07:21,708 --> 01:07:24,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大王，我们发现白晶晶昏倒山崖</font></font></font>

1148
01:07:24,125 --> 01:07:25,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">菩提老祖重伤不治</font></font></font>

1149
01:07:28,458 --> 01:07:29,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">天助我也！</font></font></font>

1150
01:07:32,083 --> 01:07:33,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">进去！</font></font></font>

1151
01:07:35,125 --> 01:07:36,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你不说出来</font></font></font>

1152
01:07:36,042 --> 01:07:37,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这一辈子都别指望出去</font></font></font>

1153
01:07:40,208 --> 01:07:41,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">懒得理你</font></font></font>

1154
01:07:47,083 --> 01:07:49,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">地也不是那么硬，有办法</font></font></font>

1155
01:07:53,708 --> 01:07:55,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">盖世魔王，神功护体</font></font></font>

1156
01:07:57,625 --> 01:07:58,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我把你伤治好</font></font></font>

1157
01:07:58,917 --> 01:08:01,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你要带我去盘丝洞找托世的猴子</font></font></font>

1158
01:08:01,417 --> 01:08:02,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我就可以找到唐僧</font></font></font>

1159
01:08:03,083 --> 01:08:04,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">到时候吃唐僧肉少不了你的份</font></font></font>

1160
01:08:05,000 --> 01:08:07,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">否则我要你死得比现在痛苦十倍</font></font></font>

1161
01:08:12,333 --> 01:08:14,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">挖隧道我也要离开这里</font></font></font>

1162
01:08:19,000 --> 01:08:21,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">借助月亮光华可以穿梭时空</font></font></font>

1163
01:08:25,375 --> 01:08:26,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">什么东西呀？</font></font></font>

1164
01:08:44,583 --> 01:08:46,916
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">般若波罗密，是梵文啊</font></font></font>

1165
01:08:48,750 --> 01:08:50,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">月光宝盒</font></font></font>

1166
01:08:53,125 --> 01:08:54,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">盘丝大仙留下来的宝物？</font></font></font>

1167
01:09:24,417 --> 01:09:26,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快带我进盘丝洞</font></font></font>

1168
01:09:30,500 --> 01:09:31,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怎么肚子有点痛呀？</font></font></font>

1169
01:09:33,833 --> 01:09:34,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把我转那儿去了？</font></font></font>

1170
01:09:34,750 --> 01:09:35,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这么多机关？</font></font></font>

1171
01:09:35,708 --> 01:09:36,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">越走越湿呢！</font></font></font>

1172
01:10:16,292 --> 01:10:17,834
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">大王，你回来了？</font></font></font>

1173
01:10:30,458 --> 01:10:31,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">撞鬼啦我</font></font></font>

1174
01:10:33,417 --> 01:10:35,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你装成这个样子干什么？</font></font></font>

1175
01:10:36,167 --> 01:10:37,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你喜欢唐三藏</font></font></font>

1176
01:10:37,708 --> 01:10:39,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我扮成他让你开心嘛</font></font></font>

1177
01:10:40,000 --> 01:10:41,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你干什么嘛？</font></font></font>

1178
01:10:41,167 --> 01:10:42,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我帮你接生呀</font></font></font>

1179
01:10:43,333 --> 01:10:44,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">头出来了</font></font></font>

1180
01:10:44,792 --> 01:10:46,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是吗？我怎么没感觉？</font></font></font>

1181
01:10:46,167 --> 01:10:47,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你看啦？</font></font></font>

1182
01:10:47,333 --> 01:10:48,666
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">原来是我的菠萝盖！</font></font></font>

1183
01:10:48,708 --> 01:10:50,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">怪不得没有头发啦</font></font></font>

1184
01:10:50,375 --> 01:10:51,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">有人来了</font></font></font>

1185
01:10:51,625 --> 01:10:53,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">先躲一躲，躲一躲！</font></font></font>

1186
01:10:57,500 --> 01:10:58,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好痛呀</font></font></font>

1187
01:10:58,500 --> 01:11:00,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我也好痛呀</font></font></font>

1188
01:11:00,458 --> 01:11:02,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">求求你把你的你放开好不好？</font></font></font>

1189
01:11:13,875 --> 01:11:14,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">观世音</font></font></font>

1190
01:11:16,958 --> 01:11:19,458
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孙悟空，你当年罪恶滔天</font></font></font>

1191
01:11:19,500 --> 01:11:22,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">希望你今生会大彻大悟，痛改前非</font></font></font>

1192
01:11:23,000 --> 01:11:23,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁在说话？</font></font></font>

1193
01:11:25,625 --> 01:11:28,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">五百年前你师父唐三藏为了赎你一命</font></font></font>

1194
01:11:28,958 --> 01:11:30,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">牺牲了他自己</font></font></font>

1195
01:11:30,500 --> 01:11:32,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">玉皇大帝特意安排你</font></font></font>

1196
01:11:32,125 --> 01:11:34,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">五百年后重投人间</font></font></font>

1197
01:11:34,208 --> 01:11:35,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">希望你能学你师父一样</font></font></font>

1198
01:11:35,833 --> 01:11:37,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">舍己为人</font></font></font>

1199
01:11:37,375 --> 01:11:39,625
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把你过往的一切罪孽洗清</font></font></font>

1200
01:11:40,458 --> 01:11:42,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">只要你肯自愿带上金刚圈</font></font></font>

1201
01:11:42,792 --> 01:11:44,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">肯改过自新</font></font></font>

1202
01:11:44,417 --> 01:11:47,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你就可以变回法力无边的齐天大圣</font></font></font>

1203
01:11:47,542 --> 01:11:50,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">到时候你就要负起取西经的重任</font></font></font>

1204
01:11:50,083 --> 01:11:51,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把历史重改</font></font></font>

1205
01:11:51,750 --> 01:11:54,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不过从此人间一切与你无关</font></font></font>

1206
01:11:54,458 --> 01:11:57,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">再不可能有半点情欲，半点留恋</font></font></font>

1207
01:11:57,333 --> 01:11:58,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">要全心归依我佛</font></font></font>

1208
01:11:59,792 --> 01:12:02,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你还没变成真正的孙悟空托世</font></font></font>

1209
01:12:02,542 --> 01:12:03,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">只系因为你还没遇上</font></font></font>

1210
01:12:03,958 --> 01:12:05,416
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">那个给你三颗痣你的人</font></font></font>

1211
01:12:06,042 --> 01:12:07,542
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">当你遇到他之后</font></font></font>

1212
01:12:07,583 --> 01:12:09,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你的一生就会改变</font></font></font>

1213
01:12:10,250 --> 01:12:11,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">跟我说话吗？</font></font></font>

1214
01:12:12,167 --> 01:12:13,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不是跟我说的吧？</font></font></font>

1215
01:12:14,500 --> 01:12:16,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">认错人啦</font></font></font>

1216
01:12:18,625 --> 01:12:19,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">神经病！</font></font></font>

1217
01:12:19,792 --> 01:12:23,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">好痛呀…　﹣放手呀</font></font></font>

1218
01:12:23,958 --> 01:12:27,000
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你安静点行不行？　﹣不行…</font></font></font>

1219
01:12:27,042 --> 01:12:30,334
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">安静呀</font></font></font>

1220
01:12:30,375 --> 01:12:32,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">呀！好痛呀</font></font></font>

1221
01:12:32,292 --> 01:12:33,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我也一样痛呀！</font></font></font>

1222
01:12:41,500 --> 01:12:42,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">小心机关</font></font></font>

1223
01:12:44,375 --> 01:12:45,292
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">追</font></font></font>

1224
01:12:46,000 --> 01:12:46,958
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走呀</font></font></font>

1225
01:12:47,083 --> 01:12:48,291
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">快拉住我呀</font></font></font>

1226
01:12:50,458 --> 01:12:52,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">抓住了…，生了…</font></font></font>

1227
01:12:54,875 --> 01:12:56,375
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">唐三藏出世了，快找</font></font></font>

1228
01:12:56,417 --> 01:12:57,250
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是！</font></font></font>

1229
01:13:02,208 --> 01:13:04,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是男的！长得很像你呀</font></font></font>

1230
01:13:07,875 --> 01:13:08,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我觉得</font></font></font>

1231
01:13:09,542 --> 01:13:11,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">做不做神仙</font></font></font>

1232
01:13:11,167 --> 01:13:13,167
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">能不能吃到唐僧肉并不重要</font></font></font>

1233
01:13:14,292 --> 01:13:16,959
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">最重要的是我们以后能好好的生活</font></font></font>

1234
01:13:17,583 --> 01:13:18,583
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把孩大带大</font></font></font>

1235
01:13:19,167 --> 01:13:20,709
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不要像我一样当山贼</font></font></font>

1236
01:13:22,000 --> 01:13:23,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你那么想要唐僧</font></font></font>

1237
01:13:24,000 --> 01:13:25,833
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">干脆儿子就叫做三藏好了</font></font></font>

1238
01:13:27,750 --> 01:13:28,708
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">谁？</font></font></font>

1239
01:13:28,750 --> 01:13:30,083
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我们可算是冤家路窄了</font></font></font>

1240
01:13:30,708 --> 01:13:31,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你想怎么样？</font></font></font>

1241
01:13:33,833 --> 01:13:34,791
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">孩子是你的？</font></font></font>

1242
01:13:36,875 --> 01:13:39,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">没错，是我跟至尊宝生的</font></font></font>

1243
01:13:41,083 --> 01:13:42,041
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说什么？</font></font></font>

1244
01:13:44,667 --> 01:13:46,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">奶妈，你告诉她吧！</font></font></font>

1245
01:13:48,000 --> 01:13:48,792
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你说呀！</font></font></font>

1246
01:13:55,125 --> 01:13:55,917
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">是！</font></font></font>

1247
01:13:58,250 --> 01:14:00,333
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">她跟至尊宝生的</font></font></font>

1248
01:14:04,750 --> 01:14:05,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">走</font></font></font>

1249
01:14:08,042 --> 01:14:09,417
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">看你往哪跑？</font></font></font>

1250
01:14:09,458 --> 01:14:10,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">不用怕，我保护你</font></font></font>

1251
01:14:11,042 --> 01:14:12,042
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你知不知道你什么身份啊？</font></font></font>

1252
01:14:12,083 --> 01:14:13,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">凭什么保护我？</font></font></font>

1253
01:14:13,583 --> 01:14:14,500
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">滚开</font></font></font>

1254
01:14:14,667 --> 01:14:15,584
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把我儿子抱走</font></font></font>

1255
01:14:20,083 --> 01:14:23,208
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">我爱妳呀！</font></font></font>

1256
01:14:23,625 --> 01:14:24,750
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">把唐三藏给我</font></font></font>

1257
01:14:25,000 --> 01:14:27,125
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">这是我儿子呀，不是唐三藏</font></font></font>

1258
01:14:27,750 --> 01:14:28,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">救命呀</font></font></font>

1259
01:14:30,542 --> 01:14:31,667
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">救命呀…</font></font></font>

1260
01:14:32,708 --> 01:14:35,541
<font size="0" color="#000000">{\an7}<font size="54"><font color="#ffffff">你这么关心我，我愿意为你精尽人亡</font></font></font>

